LuaFunction.Name: NOBN_ocs_FDVBaneData_EHLEDKategoriFromVariant()
LuaFunction.Formula: function NOBN_ocs_FDVBaneData_EHLEDKategoriFromVariant() if Variant == "AT-line (PL)" then return "Line" elseif Variant == "AT-kabel (PL)" then return "Kabel" elseif Variant == "AT-line (NL)" then return "Line" elseif Variant == "AT-kabel (NL)" then return "Kabel" elseif Variant == "Fjernline" then return "Line" elseif Variant == "Fjernkabel" then return "Kabel" elseif Variant == "Forbigangsline" then return "Line" elseif Variant == "Forbigangskabel" then return "Kabel" elseif Variant == "Forsterkningsline" then return "Line" elseif Variant == "Forsterkningskabel" then return "Kabel" elseif Variant == "Mateline" then return "Line" elseif Variant == "Matekabel" then return "Kabel" elseif Variant == "Returline" then return "Line" elseif Variant == "Returkabel" then return "Kabel" end end

LuaFunction.Name: NOBN_ocs_FDVBaneData_EHLEDFunksjonFromVariant()
LuaFunction.Formula: function NOBN_ocs_FDVBaneData_EHLEDFunksjonFromVariant() if Variant == "AT-line (PL)" then return "AT (PL/NL)" elseif Variant == "AT-kabel (PL)" then return "AT (PL/NL)" elseif Variant == "AT-line (NL)" then return "AT (PL/NL)" elseif Variant == "AT-kabel (NL)" then return "AT (PL/NL)" elseif Variant == "Fjernline" then return "Fjern" elseif Variant == "Fjernkabel" then return "Fjern" elseif Variant == "Forbigangsline" then return "Forbigang" elseif Variant == "Forbigangskabel" then return "Forbigang" elseif Variant == "Forsterkningsline" then return "Forsterkning" elseif Variant == "Forsterkningskabel" then return "Forsterkning" elseif Variant == "Mateline" then return "Mating" elseif Variant == "Matekabel" then return "Mating" elseif Variant == "Returline" then return "Return" elseif Variant == "Returkabel" then return "Retur" end end

LuaFunction.Name: NOBN_ocs_GetClosestOcsPoleToPoint()
LuaFunction.Description: Gets closest '"..rctype_OcsPole.."' or '"..rctype_TunnelWallFixing.."' object within MaxDistance of point
LuaFunction.Formula:
function NOBN_ocs_GetClosestOcsPoleToPoint(point, MaxDistance) local minDistance = MaxDistance or 10 local npo = getNearbyPointObjects2D(point, minDistance) local closest
for i = 0,npo.Count -1 do local obj = npo[i] local distance = RC__getDistance2D(npo[i].geoCoord, point) if npo[i] and npo[i].RcType == rctype_OcsPole and distance < minDistance then minDistance = distance closest = obj end end if not closest then for i = 0,npo.Count -1 do local obj = npo[i] local distance = RC__getDistance2D(npo[i].geoCoord, point) if npo[i] and npo[i].RcType == rctype_TunnelWallFixing and distance < minDistance then minDistance = distance closest = obj end end end return closest and closest.FDVBaneDataObjektID end
